{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"d0c4e177fc624a3215fb2a4ad8a4e4aa87988dfc58bba991979cea55cd8da326","slug":"from-executor-to-manager","location":"/tutorial/management/from_executor_to_manager.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"从执行者到管理者","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/tutorial/management/from_executor_to_manager.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/tutorial/management/from_executor_to_manager.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"from_executor_to_manager.md","url":"/from_executor_to_man-9d0d89f74387e3ce4a7b3b4bf346940b.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"管理者脱产与思维跃迁，是从具体业务中提炼出来的。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"Q4GbYAskFl"}],"key":"aZvT9o3x2X"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"价值创造视角","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"ZERS8mfLpZ"}],"identifier":"id","label":"价值创造视角","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"Y5X7apl3cI"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"员工视角关注个人产出，衡量标准是个人效率和任务完成度。管理层视角关注组织能力构建，衡量标准是团队的系统能力。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"d44cBJkfwY"}],"key":"WcLQE9LqHP"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把经验提炼成 SOP（离职工作章程），就是把个人的隐性经验转化为组织的显性资产。管理层不再追求自己做题最快，而是追求编写出最高效的解题大纲。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"nkVEdDGZPg"}],"key":"WUZBsVmaC9"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"冲突博弈视角","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"wj1bj8TwME"}],"identifier":"id","label":"冲突博弈视角","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"yECGtggJAs"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"员工视角遇到问题第一反应是自己冲上去解决，容易陷入情绪消耗和事务性缠斗。管理层视角遇到问题第一反应是判断「这是谁的事」「应该用什么机制解决」，必须保持超然，不能轻易下场。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"MkO9EQTWlc"}],"key":"WLbeuuGliZ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"培养新人去斗老人，而不是自己下场。管理层要当裁判，而不是选手。一旦变成选手，就失去裁判的威信和全局视野。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"IMAfDzxfrs"}],"key":"TtXCjEYsiT"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"风险感知视角","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"mSdwGiaZ81"}],"identifier":"id","label":"风险感知视角","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"GdDdXVynJr"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"员工视角的痛点是具象和短期的，感受到工作量的增加和情绪上的烦躁。管理层视角的痛点是抽象和长期的，感受到系统性脆弱。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"JoIaCCHNGO"}],"key":"wtqSBVZbnU"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"面对同一个离职事件，管理层看到的潜在问题比员工多。员工视角是向前看，看眼前障碍；管理层视角是向后看，看蝴蝶效应。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"v0ceiZtVcd"}],"key":"zRvPuO82ao"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"资源分配视角","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"P1PnYOEHWW"}],"identifier":"id","label":"资源分配视角","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"hvC1snLJ7E"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"员工视角工作是一张待办清单，按时间先后或领导安排线性推进。管理层视角工作是一个能量场，哪里混乱程度高，资源就应该优先投向哪里。","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"wQhRJrqcuW"}],"key":"qzEfENGmNg"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"离职工作属于混乱程度比较高的，那么章程的优先级也比较高。管理层不是在处理单一任务，而是通过制度建设降低整个系统的熵（混乱度）。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"mqAP9n4nAB"}],"key":"fcprWgJlXa"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"知识传递视角","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"Yhd8u55VgN"}],"identifier":"id","label":"知识传递视角","html_id":"id-4","implicit":true,"key":"YVEQdA8IZE"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"员工视角遇到管理问题习惯寻找宏大理论和底层逻辑，但落不了地。管理层视角理论只解决知不知的问题，实操才解决行不行的问题。管理的难处全在实操的颗粒度里。","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"Zi7CqkapHu"}],"key":"BgD6tRoRXr"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 给的都是道层面的东西，术它似乎不擅长。为什么 AI 不擅长？因为实操高度依赖具体上下文。管理层的工作就是在这个充满噪音的上下文里，打磨出可执行的实操。","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"mFgeywgMLE"}],"key":"U8JSjwa0bs"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"总结","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"SMWAHbgOym"}],"identifier":"id","label":"总结","html_id":"id-5","implicit":true,"key":"i9xtx6KRP9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"管理层的进阶，本质上是一场权力的让渡与痛感的转移：把具体做事的权力让渡给下属，通过 SOP 和教练式指导；把深层风险的痛感转移到自己身上，所以看到的问题总比员工多。同时坚决克制「下场替他们干」的冲动。","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"SZ4vkAvUWE"}],"key":"aHUpYagWVY"}],"key":"JlClf7SD4N"}],"key":"aiksSYBoju"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}